Thiele and Ladiges preferred to give series rank to the subclades, rather than the entire clade, so they transferred the taxa of the second clade into [[Banksia ser. Ochraceae|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Ochraceae'']], retaining only the taxa of the first clade in ''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Cyrtostylis''. ''B.&nbsp;epica''<span/>'s placement under [[Thiele and Ladiges' taxonomic arrangement of Banksia|Thiele and Ladiges' arrangement]] may be summarised as follows:<ref name="Thiele 1996"/>
:'''''[[Banksia]]'''''
::[[Banksia subg. Isostylis|''B.''&nbsp;subg. ''Isostylis'']] (3 species)
::''[[Banksia elegans|B.&nbsp;elegans]]'' (''incertae sedis'')
::'''[[Banksia subg. Banksia|''B.''&nbsp;subg. ''Banksia'']]'''
:::[[Banksia ser. Tetragonae|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Tetragonae'']] (4 species)
:::[[Banksia ser. Lindleyanae|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Lindleyanae'']] (1 species)
:::[[Banksia ser. Banksia|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Banksia'']] (2 subseries, 12 species)
:::''[[Banksia baueri|B.&nbsp;baueri]]'' (''incertae sedis'')
:::''[[Banksia lullfitzii|B.&nbsp;lullfitzii]]'' (''incertae sedis'')
:::''[[Banksia attenuata|B.&nbsp;attenuata]]'' (''incertae sedis'')
:::''[[Banksia ashbyi|B.&nbsp;ashbyi]]'' (''incertae sedis'')
:::''[[Banksia coccinea|B.&nbsp;coccinea]]'' (''incertae sedis'')
:::[[Banksia ser. Prostratae|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Prostratae'']] (8 species)
:::'''[[Banksia ser. Cyrtostylis|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Cyrtostylis'']]
::::''[[Banksia pilostylis|B.&nbsp;pilostylis]]''
::::''[[Banksia media|B.&nbsp;media]]''
::::'''''B.&nbsp;epica'''''
::::''[[Banksia praemorsa|B.&nbsp;praemorsa]]''
:::[[Banksia ser. Ochraceae|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Ochraceae'']] (3 species, 2 subspecies)
:::[[Banksia ser. Grandes|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Grandes'']] (2 species)
:::[[Banksia ser. Salicinae|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Salicinae'']] (2 series, 11 species, 4 subspecies)
:::[[Banksia ser. Spicigerae|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Spicigerae'']] (3 series, 7 species, 6 varieties)
:::[[Banksia ser. Quercinae|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Quercinae'']] (2 species)
:::[[Banksia ser. Dryandroideae|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Dryandroideae'']] (1 species)
:::[[Banksia ser. Abietinae|''B.''&nbsp;ser. ''Abietinae'']] (4 subseries, 15 species, 8 varieties)

The arrangement of Thiele and Ladiges was not accepted by George, and was discarded in his 1999 revision. 
Under [[George's taxonomic arrangement of Banksia|George's 1999 arrangement]], ''B.&nbsp;epica''<span/>'s placement was as follows:
